item.title: CVE-2024-36454|2024-07-16T18:27:45.717Z -- fsas%20technologies%20inc. -- ipcom%20ex2%20series%20%28v01l0x%20series%29
item.description: Use of uninitialized resource issue exists in IPCOM EX2 Series (V01L0x Series) V01L07NF0201 and earlier, and IPCOM VE2 Series V01L07NF0201 and earlier. If this vulnerability is exploited, the system may be rebooted or suspended by receiving a specially crafted packet.
